    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
     <li>100g plain flour</li>
<li>2 large eggs</li>
<li>300ml milk</li>
<li>1 tbsp sunflower or vegetable oil</li>
<li>caster sugar. to serve (optional)</li>
</ul>
<h2>Instructions</h2>
  <ol>
    <li> Mix the dry ingredients.</li> 
    <li>In a large bowl, whisk together the flour, baking powder, sugar, and salt.</li>
<li>Mix the wet ingredients. In another bowl, whisk the eggs and milk until evenly combined</li>
<li>Combine everything</li>
<li>Cook the pancakes</li>
<li>Flip and finish</li>
</ol>

